Substantial modifications by Adacor Hosting GmbH:
  - Branding and product identity (renamed to "Workplace CLI")
  - Adacor AI as default provider, Qwen 3 30B (256k) as default model
  - Local-first telemetry (originally sent to Mistral datalake)
  - Configuration directory rename (~/.vibe → ~/.config/workplace,
    .vibe/ → .workplace/)
  - Environment-variable prefix VIBE_ → WORKPLACE_

This product also includes the following skills from Anthropic's official
skills repository (https://github.com/anthropics/skills), embedded as
built-ins under `vibe/core/skills/builtins/`:
  - frontend-design  (frontend_design.py)
  - canvas-design    (canvas_design.py — `canvas-fonts/` asset bundle
                      not embedded)
  - theme-factory    (theme_factory.py — includes the 10 themes/*.md
                      files inline; theme-showcase.pdf not embedded)
  - skill-creator    (skill_creator.py — scripts/, references/, agents/,
                      eval-viewer/ asset bundles not embedded; full
                      benchmark workflow requires cloning the upstream
                      repo)

